Package: ihsMW
Title: Access Malawi Integrated Household Survey Data in R
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: person("Vitumbiko", "Kayuni",
             email = "vitumbikokayuni@gmail.com",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0008-4331-3839"))
Description: Provides programmatic access to the Malawi Integrated Household
    Survey (IHS) via the World Bank Microdata Library API. Users can search
    variables, download data for IHS rounds 2 through 5, and work with complex
    survey designs entirely from R, with no manual file management required.
